    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're a down-on-your-luck hobo in the year 30xx. It's up to you to fight back against the The Machine Augmented Neoliberals - a deranged political party obsessed with harvesting the citizens' precious flesh.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPGRADE YOUR HOBO</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a H.O.B.O. agent, your body is your weapon. Graft on your choice of parts from among a diverse array of powerful and deadly biomechanical limbs. Use your custom limbs to bludgeon your way through the hordes of horrifying machine-creatures standing between you and liberation from The M.A.N.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865270/extras/03eb3c2d2df1a9f20d0a1b95df5cfdbc.poster.avif?t=1768306790\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865270/extras/03eb3c2d2df1a9f20d0a1b95df5cfdbc.webm?t=1768306790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865270/extras/03eb3c2d2df1a9f20d0a1b95df5cfdbc.mp4?t=1768306790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1-4 PLAYER CHAOS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go solo or team up with friends in co-op as you complete missions, recruit allies, and do everything you can to avoid violent dismemberment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865270/extras/d9a8cccaf94ed1cd4dfe387f63547dfb.poster.avif?t=1768306790\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865270/extras/d9a8cccaf94ed1cd4dfe387f63547dfb.webm?t=1768306790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865270/extras/d9a8cccaf94ed1cd4dfe387f63547dfb.mp4?t=1768306790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVEL EDITOR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the in-game, no-code Level Editor to create your own special brand of carnage. Play and create endless community content using full Steam Workshop integration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865270/extras/a510ba5211a7ce5f2d31fc5782daec11.poster.avif?t=1768306790\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865270/extras/a510ba5211a7ce5f2d31fc5782daec11.webm?t=1768306790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865270/extras/a510ba5211a7ce5f2d31fc5782daec11.mp4?t=1768306790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
